Title: The Spectacular Collapse of CryptoKitties, the First Big Blockchain Game
Description: In September 2018, someone bought an angry cartoon cat for the equivalent $170,000. It was  big win for CryptoKitties, the world’s first blockchain gaming hit. But the sky-high transaction obscured a more difficult truth: CryptoKitties was dying.

Title: The next big step: Godot 4.0 reaches Beta
Description: It has been a long road to Godot 4.0 with 17 alpha builds distributed in 2022, and continuous development effort since 2019. We aren’t done yet, but today marks a major milestone on the road to Godot 4.0: the first beta is out!
